			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				My Barbarian warrior character gained levels REALLY fast in everfrost peaks. I got level 2 in just half an hour. I don't have much advice for playing a barbarian warriror except you can fight in blackburrow once you hit level 4, though i wouldnt suggest it until level 5.
